cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language text and computational models for understanding narratives. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves tracking and predicting outcomes, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
